$OPPE Revision Session

#OPPE Format
- 5 Questions
- 2 hours
- No options
- Equal weightage

#Important Topics
- Extracting patterns from lines using `grep -o`
- Converting uppercase to lowercase using `tr`
- Sort and Unique
- Bash Functions
- Common numeric functions, factorial, fibonacci, prime
- Pattern matching in bash
- Loops, break, continue, exit, return
- Heredoc, Herestring
- Sed basics, print, delete, `-n`
- Awk, associative arrays, counts and maps
